                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The function returns a string that represents the fiscal year period. The structure of this return value typically includes the fiscal year and period number, formatted as a string (e.g., \"FY2023-P01\")."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
